      • JsonItem

      • JsonItem

        public JsonItem(com.poesys.db.pk.json.JsonPrimaryKey primaryKey,
                java.lang.Double amount,
                java.lang.Boolean debit,
                java.lang.Boolean checked,
                com.poesys.db.pk.json.JsonPrimaryKey accountKey,
                java.lang.String accountName,
                java.util.List<com.poesys.db.pk.json.JsonPrimaryKey> receivableKeys,
                java.util.List<JsonReimbursement> receivableReimbursements,
                java.util.List<com.poesys.db.pk.json.JsonPrimaryKey> reimbursingItemKeys,
                java.util.List<JsonReimbursement> reimbursingItemsReimbursements)
        Create a JsonItem.
        Parameters:
        primaryKey - the JSON primary key for the item
        amount - the monetary amount in dollars of the transaction item
        debit - whether the item is a debit (true) or credit (false); default value is the debit-default value of the account
        checked - whether the value and details of the transaction item have been verified and reconciled
        accountName - name of the account for the item
        receivableKeys - a list of the primary keys for receivable items for this reimbursement, if this is a reimbursement; otherwise, null
        receivableReimbursements - a list of the primary keys for reimbursements for this receivable, if this is a receivable; otherwise, null
        reimbursingItemKeys - a list of the primary keys for the association objects linked to this receivable item; null if not a receivable item
        reimbursingItemsReimbursements - a list of the primary keys for the association objects linked to this reimbursing item; null if not a reimbursing item
